<h1 id="process-collection-letters" sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="29">Process collection letters</h1>


<p sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">This topic shows how to create, print, and post collection letters. This task uses the USMF demo company.</p>
<h2 id="set-up-a-collection-letter-sequence-on-the-posting-profile" sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="35">Set up a collection letter sequence on the posting profile</h2>
