<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Navigation pane &gt; Modules &gt; Credit and collections &gt; Setup &gt; Customer posting profiles</strong>.</li>
