<li sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Expand the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Table restrictions</strong> tab to change the way that collection letters are processed. If this field is set to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/accounts-receivable/tasks/process-collection-letters.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Yes</strong>, then collection letters will be created for this posting profile.</li>
